== Headline ==

The central [[abstraction]] in [[functional programming]]
== Illustration ==

Consider the following [[function definition]] in [[Language:Haskell]].

<syntaxhighlight language="haskell">
-- The increment function
inc :: Int -> Int
inc x = x + 1
</syntaxhighlight>

This [[function]] can be applied, for example, to the [[argument]] 41 as follows.

<syntaxhighlight language="haskell">
inc 41
</syntaxhighlight>

This [[function application]] is evaluated to the following [[result]]:

<pre>
42
</pre>
